  "name": "Release Notes - 3.12.11 - Inventory Planning API",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"release-notes-3-12-11-inventory-planning-api\">Release Notes - 3.12.11 - Inventory Planning API</h1>\n<p><span><strong>Release Date: </strong>13th January 2021</span></p>\n<p>In this release we've added two new fields to the \"GetProductsDetailed\" method and will be deprecating/retiring an older field.</p>\n<h3 data-id=\"getproductsdetailed-new-fields\">GetProductsDetailed - New fields </h3>\n<p>The new fields are as follows:</p>\n<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>Field Name</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p><strong>Details</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">IsDisabled</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p>Indicates whether a product is marked as \"Disabled\"</p>\n<p><img alt=\"mceclip2 (62).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppd5LEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">PreventDisabling</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p>Indicates if the product has the \"Prevent Disabling\" option enabled (used to control whether stock is disabled in web store integrations once they're out of stock)</p>\n<p><img alt=\"mceclip1 - 2023-07-09T135042.868.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppbk8EAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 data-id=\"getproductsdetailed-deprecated-fields\">GetProductsDetailed - Deprecated Fields</h3>\n<p>The field \"<strong>DisableProduct</strong>\" was used to indicate the \"Prevent Disabling\" setting within Retail Express and not used to control whether the product was disabled, causing a bit of confusion.</p>\n<p>To improve the API we have introduced two new fields as per above.</p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>The field \"DisableProduct\" has been deprecated but is currently fully functional. We recommend updating your API integrations to utilise the two new fields.</p>\n</div>",
